zation of  James Lovelock's  conception of the whole earthly ecosystem as a living self-regulating entity under this name."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Gaïa De Bas was born about 1145, her father, Ponç II de Cervera, Vescomte de Bas, was 32 and her mother, Almodis de Barcelona, was 20. She had at least 1 son with Ramon de Torreja."},"et":{"Abt 1145–":"umbes 1145–Surnud","1139–1187":"1139–1187","1145–Female":"1145–Surnud","–1180":"–1180","1130–1195":"1130–1195","1177–1195":"1177–1195","1115–1155":"1115–1155","1126–1175":"1126–1175","1187":"1187","1175":"1175","1130":"1130","1195":"1195","1180":"1180","1139":"1139","1126":"1126","1115":"1115","1147":"1147","Abt 1145":"umbes 1145","1145":"1145","1177":"1177","1155":"1155","Solsona, Catalogne, Espagne":"Bisbat de Solsona, Catalunya, Hispaania"},"fi":{"Abt 1145–":"noin 1145–Kuollut","1139–1187":"1139–1187","1145–Female":"1145–Kuollut","–1180":"–1180","1130–1195":"1130–1195","1177–1195":"1177–1195","1115–1155":"1115–1155","1126–1175":"1126–1175","1187":"1187","1175":"1175","1130":"1130","1195":"1195","1180":"1180","1139":"1139","1126":"1126","1115":"1115","1147":"1147","Abt 1145":"noin 1145","1145":"1145","1177":"1177","1155":"1155","Solsona, Catalogne, Espagne":"Bisbat de Solsona, Catalunya, Espanja"},"fr":{"Abt 1145–":"environ 1145–Décédée","1139–1187":"1139–1187","1145–Female":"1145–Décédée","–1180":"–1180","1130–1195":"1130–1195","1177–1195":"1177–1195","1115–1155":"1115–1155","1126–1175":"1126–1175","1187":"1187","1175":"1175","1130":"1130","1195":"1195","1180":"1180","1139":"1139","1126":"1126","1115":"1115","1147":"1147","Abt 1145":"environ 1145","1145":"1145","1177":"1177","1155":"1155","Solsona, Catalogne, Espagne":"Bisbat de Solsona, Catalunya, Espagne","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Gaïa De Bas est née environ 1145, son père, Ponç II de Cervera, Vescomte de Bas, avait 32 ans et sa mère, Almodis de Barcelona, avait 20 ans. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Ramon de Torreja."},"de":{"Abt 1145–":"um 1145–Verstorben"